妈妈 拉夫的家人没法保护他
Mom, Raf's family can't protect him.

51
00:04:42,500 --> 00:04:44,080
不会像他们这样
Not like they can.

52
00:04:44,190 --> 00:04:48,000
琼 我为自己的失败感到十分懊悔
June, it deeply grieves me that I have failed.

53
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:51,680
但我会尽我的一切所能来确保…
But I will do everything in my power to ensure

54
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:58,440
