not their own survival!

59
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:14,040
妈妈 黑暗能量正从地下向外井喷
Mom, Dark Energon is pouring out of the Earth.

60
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,490
这不正常
It doesn't do that.

61
00:05:15,690 --> 00:05:17,180
可能关系到所有人的性命
This could be about everyone's survival

62
00:05:17,180 --> 00:05:18,410
不光是我们的
not just ours.

63
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:19,230
你们必须跟我走
You're coming with me

64
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,510
三个人都走
all three of you.

65
00:05:20,660 --> 00:05:22,980
他们不会再回来了
And they will not be coming back.

66
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,650
我理解
I understand.

67
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,580
这就完了？
That's it?

68
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:32,050
同甘共苦这么久 一句“再见”就打发了？
After all we've been through together, "see ya"?

69
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:34,250
我们不是可以自由选择吗？
What about our freedom to choose?

70
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,810
那是他们星球的东西
That may fly on their planet

71
00:05:35,930 --> 00:05:37,500
在地球上行不通
but not here on Earth.

72
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,750
上车
Get in.

73
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:44,750
你以为我会坐一辆不会变形的汽车吗？
Do you really expect me to ride in a non-transforming vehicle?

74
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:46,720
神子 我是认真的
Miko, I'm serious.

75
00:05:46,890 --> 00:05:48,140
你又不是我妈
You're not my mother.

76
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,380
神子…
Miko...

77
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,780
你也不是！
Neither are you!

78
00:05:52,110 --> 00:05:53,560
好吧 我是你妈对吧
Well, I am yours.

79
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,040
我们走 杰克
Let's go, Jack.

80
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:01,740
她毕竟是你妈妈
She is your mom.

81
