救护车 启动环陆桥
Ratchet, activate the GroundBridge.

84
00:06:27,370 --> 00:06:28,710
谢了 不必
No, thank you.

85
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,330
擎天柱 能收到吗？
Prime, do you copy?

86
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:50,420
听到了 福勒探员
I hear you, Agent Fowler.

87
00:06:50,550 --> 00:06:51,770
看新闻了吗？
Been watching the news?

88
00:06:51,890 --> 00:06:54,190
大自然母亲的鼻孔发痒了
Mother nature's got a twitch in her breaches.

89
00:06:54,310 --> 00:06:56,020
我们知道火山喷发的事
We know about the volcano.

90
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,220
那地震呢？
And the quakes?

91
00:06:57,370 --> 00:07:02,860
七次大地震的震级分毫不差 而且跟火山喷发的时间完全吻合
Seven major temblors of the exact the same magnitude at the exact same time as the volcanic eruption.

92
00:07:02,980 --> 00:07:08,730
地震分布在全球各个火山岩板块 按理说毫不相干 可它们却在…
All over the globe on different plutonic plates, in theory unrelated, if they hadn't happened...

93
00:07:08,880 --> 00:07:11,280
同一时刻爆发
At the exact same time.

94
00:07:11,460 --> 00:07:13,770
来看看 还有好消息
Check it out, more good news.

95
00:07:13,910 --> 00:07:16,470
可怕的风暴让当地人目瞪口呆
Freak storms unlike any the region has seen

96
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,830
海啸使加拿大沿岸岌岌可危
tsunamis threaten the Canadian coast

97
00:07:18,850 --> 00:07:21,210
