while lightning storms pummel the Gobi Desert.

98
00:07:21,340 --> 00:07:25,640
与此同时 电磁异常现象在城市电网中蔓延
Meanwhile, electro-magnetic anomalies plague urban power grids.

99
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:30,980
这些全球性的反常现象引发众人追问：\N怎么会这样 还能怎么样？
These abnormal global phenomena are leaving most to wonder: why now, and what next?

100
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,840
别告诉我 虎子们造了个天气控制仪
Don't tell me your 'Cons've built a weather machine.

101
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:35,030
