One that powerful?

102
00:07:35,150 --> 00:07:36,430
基本不可能
Highly unlikely.

103
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:43,270
我认为 黑暗能量在这个节骨眼上出现 决不是巧合
I do not believe the appearance of Dark Energon at this point in time to be coincidental.

104
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:51,270
一秒钟 两秒钟…
One 100, two 100...

105
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:53,170
你还好吧 拉夫？
You OK back there, Raf?

106
00:07:53,670 --> 00:07:55,040
我看见闪电了
I saw lightning.

107
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:56,620
所以在数秒 等雷声…
I'm counting until the thunder...

108
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:59,530
嗯哼 看来要起风暴了
Huh, looks like a storm.

109
00:07:59,650 --> 00:08:01,120
我的花园可遭殃了
My garden will love it.

110
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:20,610
拉夫 你没事吧？
Raf, are you ok?

111
00:08:20,610 --> 00:08:21,420
嗯
Hmm.

112
00:08:21,750 --> 00:08:23,100
那是什么？
What's that?

113
00:08:29,230 --> 00:08:30,730
不…
No.

114
00:08:49,880 --> 00:08:52,170
快点 快点 快点！
Come on, come on, come on!

115
00:09:33,390 --> 00:09:36,030
小蜂让咱们爬到他手上！
Bee wants us to climb into his hand.

116
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:07,460
谢谢
Thank you.

117
00:10:09,140 --> 00:10:12,030
他说“不客气”
He says "You are welcome."

118
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:36,850
喷涌你的生命之血 从深渊中崛起 和我融为一体！
Reverse of your very life blood rising from the depth to become one with me.

119
00:10:57,430 --> 00:10:59,070
我们回来了
We are back.

120
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:02,560
我们也放心了
And we are glad.

121
00:11:05,490 --> 00:11:06,600
你还好吗？
Are you alright?

122
00:11:07,310 --> 00:11:09,590
我会好起来的 杰克…
I will be. Jack...

123
00:11:09,590 --> 00:11:10,720
妈妈 我…
Mom, I...

124
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:13,220
我知道 我也是
I know, me too.

125
00:11:14,290 --> 00:11:18,450
但你得禁足到30岁…25岁吧
But you're grounded till you're 30... 25.

126
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:23,340
各国领导人将这次奇异的天气状况 定性为全球性紧急事件
World leaders are classifying these bizarre weather patterns as a global emergency.

127
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:24,820
全球性的？
Global?

128
00:11:25,040 --> 00:11:27,310
科学家们认为 该现象或多或少
And scientists believe the phenomena to be somehow

129
00:11:27,310 --> 00:11:30,010
和近期的星球串联有关
related to the current planetary alignment.

130
00:11:30,240 --> 00:11:31,420
有什么发现 擎天柱？
What have you learned, Prime?

131
00:11:31,510 --> 00:11:33,250
你最好别跟我扯淡…
And you'd better not blow smoke up my ass...

132
00:11:33,450 --> 00:11:38,890
达比小姐 真是个美丽的邂逅
Miss Darby, What a nice surprise.

133
00:11:39,010 --> 00:11:40,540
福勒探员
Special Agent Fowler.

134
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:45,650
这就是我们的发现：跟火山中所谓的岩浆一样
We have learned this: as with the so called magma from the volcano

135
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:49,640
这些地震源自地壳以下极深的位置
these earthquakes originated far below the Earth's crust...

136
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:53,740
实际上 震源就在地核的正中央
from the very center of the Earth's core in fact.

137
00:11:53,860 --> 00:11:56,340
一般的地震不是这样 对吧？
Quakes don't start there, do they?

138
00:11:56,570 --> 00:12:02,070
细微的震颤呈固定的节奏起伏 就像是…
Tiny tremors rising and falling in a consistent pattern, almost like...

139
00:12:05,730 --> 00:12:07,350
看在火种源的份上…
by the All Spark...

140
00:12:07,990 --> 00:12:12,440
如果把这些数据点 转换成声音文件的话…
If I convert these data points to audio files...

141
00:12:12,550 --> 00:12:14,240
怎么 什么东西？
What, what is it?

142
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:15,970
听
Listen.

143
00:12:36,290 --> 00:12:39,910
停 声波 关掉它！
Stop, Soundwave. Turn it off.

144
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:43,180
我的脑袋要被它震裂了！
I can still hear it pounding in my brain!

145
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:45,100
塞博特恩人的心跳？
Cybertronian heartbeat?

146
00:12:45,220 --> 00:12:46,400
这怎么可能？
How was that possible?

147
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:47,800
心脏泵的是血
A heart pumps blood.

148
00:12:47,920 --> 00:12:50,260
地球内部没有能流通的东西 除了…
There is nothing inside the Earth to pump except...

149
00:12:50,460 --> 00:12:52,490
宇宙大帝之血
Blood of Unicron.

150
00:12:59,890 --> 00:13:02,510
我苏醒了！
I awakened.

151
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,880
好吧 先打住
Ok, hold on.

152
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,930
你的意思是 地底下有个活物
You mean something's living down there

153
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:15,610
就在地球里边？
inside our planet?

154
00:13:15,740 --> 00:13:19,700
恐怕 地核并不是由岩浆组成的
I fear that the Earth's very core is not comprised of magma

155
00:13:19,830 --> 00:13:24,740
这和人类科学有出入 但应该是黑暗能量
as your science has suggested, but of Dark Energon.

156
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,770
如果我们听到的是火种
And if we're hearing a spark

157
00:13:26,910 --> 00:13:32,140
那么宇宙大帝就是崛起的黑暗势力 如预言所说
then Unicron is the rising darkness that the prophecy foretold.

158
00:13:32,300 --> 00:13:35,600
好吧 怎么才能让这东西趴着不动呢？
So how do we stop this thing from rising?

159
00:13:35,720 --> 00:13:39,020
恐怕预言对此并没有提及
That I'm afraid was not foretold.

160
00:13:39,150 --> 00:13:43,260
地核里面怎么会有别的东西呢 而且还是活的？
How can something be in our Earth core and be alive?

161
00:13:43,380 --> 00:13:46,420
这种情况不是没有先例
Such a thing is not unprecedented.

162
00:13:47,710 --> 00:13:49,560
在创世之初
Before the beginning

163
00:13:50,060 --> 00:13:53,780
世间只有原始天尊 以及宇宙大帝
there was Primus. And there was Unicron.

164
00:13:54,230 --> 00:13:56,980
一方是造物主的化身
One, the incarnation of creation

165
00:13:57,700 --> 00:14:00,940
而另一方 是毁灭的代言人
the other... of destruction.

166
00:14:03,200 --> 00:14:07,110
亘古以来 原始天尊和宇宙大帝频繁交战
For eons, Primus and Unicron battled

167
00:14:08,730 --> 00:14:13,540
二者实力不相上下 无数个回合难分胜负
the balance of power shifting between them more times than could be counted.

168
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:17,360
后来 原始天尊创造出十三位领袖――
Only by creating the Thirteen--

169
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:20,260
也就是我的几位前任领袖――
the original Primes preceded me--

170
00:14:20,780 --> 00:14:26,570
才使自己最终战胜了宇宙大帝 并将他流放
was Primus finally able to defeat Unicron and cast him out.

171
00:14:27,830 --> 00:14:31,570
原始天尊融入我们星球的核心
Primus became one with the very core of our planet

172
00:14:31,700 --> 00:14:34,890
通过火种源之井创造生命
creating life through the Well of All Sparks

173
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:42,570
而宇宙大帝从此销声匿迹 如今却重返江湖
while Unicron was never to be heard from again... until now.

174
00:14:42,830 --> 00:14:47,310
也许我们能找到这个钻地虎当年进入地心时 挖出的洞口
Maybe we can find the hole this kuggo Con left when he dug himself all the way down there

175
00:14:47,430 --> 00:14:49,510
在里面填满炸药
and fill it full of explosives.

176
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:51,010
福勒探员
Agent Fowler

177
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:54,330
我认为 并非是宇宙大帝想在地球安家
I do not believe that Earth became Unicron's home

178
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:57,620
而是随着时间推移和重力作用
but rather that with time and gravitational force

179
00:14:57,730 --> 00:15:01,260
星体碎屑聚拢在这个沉睡的巨人周围
debris collected around this slumbering titan.

180
00:15:01,690 --> 00:15:04,650
这才造就了你们的地球
Forming your Earth itself.

181
00:15:05,980 --> 00:15:11,260
他现在才睡醒 是因为星球串联形成了强大的磁吸力吗？
And he's only awakening now, due to the magnetic pull created by the planetary alignment?

182
00:15:11,370 --> 00:15:15,440
好吧 宇宙大帝用几十亿年打了个盹儿 现在要干嘛？
Ok, what happens now when Unicron wakes up from his billion-year nap?

183
00:15:15,570 --> 00:15:19,690
是啊 难道他伸个懒腰就“砰”的一声 地球灰飞烟灭了？
Yeah, does he stretch and ka-pow... Earth pup to dust?

184
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:24,750
你也不知道 对吧？
You don't know, do you?

185
00:15:25,680 --> 00:15:30,300
我猜想 宇宙大帝的身躯应该和传说中一样 硕大无比
My guess is that Unicron has transcended physical form as we know it.

186
00:15:30,370 --> 00:15:37,680
尽管如此 我们必须想办法确保这个“不可抗力”…
Nonetheless, we must find a way to ensure that this "force of nature" never fully awakens.

187
00:15:37,810 --> 00:15:41,570
你们星球的命运在此一举
The fate of your planet depends upon it.

188
00:15:42,540 --> 00:15:46,900
威震天陛下 货舱差不多被黑暗物质堆满了
Lord Megatron, our cargo hold is nearly filled with the dark substance.

189
00:15:47,020 --> 00:15:48,470
我建议收兵
I recommend a retreat

190
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:51,190
战士们受黑暗能量的影响 越来越虚弱
the troops are growing weak from its effects.

191
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:53,780
但我却感到空前强大
And yet I grow stronger.

192
00:15:54,740 --> 00:15:58,500
毒蜘蛛 你负责指挥 等我回来
Airachnid, you're in command until my return.

193
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:03,050
您这是要去哪儿 主人？
Your return from where, Master?

194
00:16:03,190 --> 00:16:06,770
去会会宇宙大帝
From my audience with Unicron.

195
00:16:25,220 --> 00:16:27,480
我感受到您的存在
I feel your presents

196
00:16:27,610 --> 00:16:29,530
分享您尊贵的火种！
share your very spark.

197
00:16:29,650 --> 00:16:33,560
我专程来拜访您 我的阁下和主人 全能的宇宙大帝！
I call on you as my Lord and Master, almighty Unicron.

198
00:16:45,290 --> 00:16:47,880
谁在和我说话？
Who would speak to me?

199
00:16:48,010 --> 00:16:49,980
您最谦卑的仆人
Your servant most humble

200
00:16:50,150 --> 00:16:53,360
威震天 霸天虎的统帅
Megatron, leader of the Decepticons

201
00:16:53,490 --> 00:16:55,100
您忠诚的使者
and your very Herald

202
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:58,630
是我运用黑暗能量 将你我联系在一起
the one who wielded the Dark Energon which binds us

203
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:03,670
使您再次苏醒 最终验证了预言！
to awaken you once again. The prophecy has been fulfilled.

204
00:17:03,870 --> 00:17:07,990
我们即将共创一番大业 强强联手！
It is only the beginning of what we shall accomplish, together!

205
00:17:08,120 --> 00:17:13,290
为您统治这颗星球 连同所有的生命 我将义不容辞！
For you shall rule this planet and those who walk upon it through me.

206
00:17:13,420 --> 00:17:15,680
痴人说梦！
Pride for fool.

207
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:21,950
你竟然以为 自己有资格召唤我的生命力？
How dare you think yourself capable of summoning my life force?

208
00:17:22,090 --> 00:17:27,500
我苏醒 是因为我感觉时机已到！
I rise because I have deemed my time.

209
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:30,820
主人 我无意以下犯上
Master, I did not mean to overstep.

210
00:17:30,950 --> 00:17:32,610
闭嘴 蠕虫！
Silence, worm!

211
00:17:32,790 --> 00:17:36,980
我无需一个下人插手此事
I have no need of your lowly assistance.

212
00:17:38,310 --> 00:17:39,580
求您了 我的陛下
Please, my Lord.

213
00:17:39,700 --> 00:17:42,510
我此生只为您效忠！
I exist only to serve you.

214
00:17:42,850 --> 00:17:45,080
这是什么味道？
What is this I sense?

215
00:17:45,210 --> 00:17:48,650
原始天尊的遗骨吗？这里也有？！
The taint of Primus? Here?!

216
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:50,120
那是擎天柱
That is Optimus

217
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:53,220
最后一个领袖 我们的死敌
the last of the Primes, our sworn enemy.

218
00:17:53,410 --> 00:17:55,690
你口口声声说对我尽忠
You profess loyalty to me

219
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:59,600
却放任原始天尊的门徒活到今天？！
yet allow a disciple of Primus to live?!

220
00:17:59,740 --> 00:18:01,500
我会为您消灭他！
I will destroy him for you!

221
00:18:01,620 --> 00:18:03,150
他的惨叫会响彻…
His screams will be heard...

222
00:18:03,150 --> 00:18:05,440
你的花言巧语我听够了
I grow weary of your prattle.

223
00:18:05,590 --> 00:18:09,200
显然 如果你有实力消灭这个领袖
Surely if you had the power to destroy this Prime

224
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:11,680
你早该做到了
you would have done so already.

225
00:18:11,810 --> 00:18:16,390
我还是亲自处理他吧
I will deal with him myself.

226
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:37,040
救护车 这个震源的特征和其他几处基本一致
Ratchet, this epicenter is consistent with the findings of the others.

227
00:18:37,150 --> 00:18:39,450
地下矿藏非常丰富
Its terrain is rich in ore.

228
00:18:39,570 --> 00:18:40,840
那是什么意思？
So what does that tell us?

229
00:18:40,970 --> 00:18:43,970
这表示 你们地球上的天然金属矿
It follows that the natural medals in your Earth

230
00:18:44,090 --> 00:18:47,570
就是宇宙大帝的扩展部分 相当于他的四肢
would be extensions of Unicron-- his limbs if you will.

231
00:18:47,690 --> 00:18:49,840
这么说 他的确伸了个懒腰
So, he did have his morning stretch

232
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:52,270
所以才引发了地震
which is why these quakes happened.

233
00:18:52,540 --> 00:18:56,090
擎天柱 我发现宇宙大帝火种的活性急剧增强
Optimus, I'm detecting a swell of Unicron's spark activity.

234
00:18:56,220 --> 00:18:57,360
放心吧 救护车
Rest assured, Ratchet

235
00:18:57,360 --> 00:18:59,790
我会提高警惕的
I will proceed with vigilance.

236
00:19:02,370 --> 00:19:06,750
你认识我吗 原始天尊的追随者？
Do you know me, follower of Primus?

237
00:19:06,890 --> 00:19:09,790
宇宙大帝 混沌制造者
Unicron, the Chaos Bringer.

238
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:12,500
很好
Good.

239
00:19:19,580 --> 00:19:27,060
现在 称我为宇宙大帝――你的毁灭者！
Now know me as Unicron, your destroyer!

240
00:19:42,360 --> 00:19:46,170
我恳求您听我一言 尊敬的宇宙大帝
I humbly request your ear, Lord Unicron.

241
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:51,410
一个如此低三下四的领袖 到底要说什么？
And what would a Prime be so compelled to say to me?

242
00:19:51,530 --> 00:19:54,080
我的请求不是为自己
I make this appeal not for myself

243
00:19:54,210 --> 00:19:59,210
而是为这个由您构建的星球 以及栖居其上的生命体
but for this planet which you constitute, and the beings who inhabit it.

244
00:19:59,370 --> 00:20:03,880
人类依赖于您 才能繁衍生息
Human kind relies upon you, for life, sustenance.

245
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:08,980
您的复活只会导致这个物种走向毁灭
Your resurrection will only result in the destruction of a spices

246
00:20:09,100 --> 00:20:12,860
而它恰恰是由您的伟大子孙孕育而生的
which evolved from the seeds of your very greatness.

247
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:16,570
那么你所说的这种人类
So this humankind of whom you speak

248
00:20:16,710 --> 00:20:18,910
它们也算是我的后裔吗？
you consider them my progeny?

249
00:20:19,060 --> 00:20:20,810
没错
Indeed.

250
00:20:21,190 --> 00:20:26,190
是寄生虫！它们也会领教到我的怒火
Parasites! They, too, shall know my wrathful hand

251
00:20:26,320 --> 00:20:29,120
但我要先和你把账算清！
once I am finished with you.

252
00:20:36,450 --> 00:20:45,030
多日不见 原始天尊的氏族竟如此衰败 今天你陨落无疑！
The line of Primus has grown weak in my absence, and thus you shall fall.

253
00:20:45,250 --> 00:20:47,540
汽车人固有一死
That outcome is inevitable

254
00:20:47,670 --> 00:20:50,160
但今天不是时候！
but not on this day.

255
00:21:13,990 --> 00:21:19,530
是的 原始天尊的门徒 就在今天
Yes, disciple of Primes, on this very day.

256
00:21:19,660 --> 00:21:26,760
宇宙大帝之名独一无二 但我们都是宇宙大帝！
For Unicron may be one, but we all are Unicron.

